{"tid":2036403,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"新機嘈到拆天問題","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:34:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-28T07:37:25.000Z","uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07d2b60546fbb918018d4515ef735637e2525dc0","tid":2036403,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:34:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n朋友冇Lihkg AC,代問<br />\n朋友換新機ASUS TUF 365M Plus MB. CPU 用 i7 9700 4.7 GHz 8 core<br />\n佢有好多report/data成日要過夜gen,個sales介紹佢用:<br />\nCooler master hyper 212 LED CPU Cooler RR 212 L 16 PR R1<br />\ni7 9700 4.7 GHz 8 core CPU<br />\nCEMAC 12 CM Case Fan<br />\n點知一開機嘈到拆天! 入BIOS見到有3把FAN,佢stop左CHA2 Fan就靜晒(見圖),有問題如下:<br />\n1) 係唔係一定要3把fan開晒?只開CPU及CHA1得唔得?<br />\n2) 如1 ok,CPU及CHA1 要set去 standard, full speed定turbo?<br />\n3) 除入bios去set之外,有咩方法可以響windows 10入邊開關啲fan? <br />\n4) 有冇app可以直頭detect一熱就自動開CHA2 fan ?<br />\n謝謝</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fA8gk7E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfA8gk7E.jpg&h=285a653d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"75e441accec62e8ff7d37299604d1964201fb015","tid":2036403,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:00:41.000Z","msg":"PWM"},{"pid":"6b23c3ca6cc6823032608630f3e2235057f9874b","tid":2036403,"uid":292644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75e441accec62e8ff7d37299604d1964201fb015","tid":2036403,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:00:41.000Z","msg":"PWM"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:13:50.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">???<br />\n咩？</span>"},{"pid":"34b2c1f0280a7d32bdac1fd9cc3210add0b1e405","tid":2036403,"uid":113922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:16:19.000Z","msg":"pwm mode ar"},{"pid":"91adc3eb5257118b1c3923606726e05293ba6aa5","tid":2036403,"uid":78143,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T13:16:59.000Z",